data.description: HARD TO FIND! This wonderful Oneonta Townhouse is located in a quiet city neighborhood. This 2 Bedroom, 2 bath home is immaculate and can be sold fully furnished with gently used furnishings if desired (ask for details) and includes the top of the line appliances . Roof is just a few years old. No need to concern yourself with cutting the lawn, or snow and garbage removal- your annual Association fee of $1210 per year takes care of that!
